en: So fast at night
zh: 天怎么快就亮了么

en: Oh fuck. Work overtime today
zh: 哦对。今天要加班

en: I have to go out quickly
zh: 要赶快出门才行啊

en: I have already arrived home，but I still have to go to work when I should have a rest.
zh: 明明都已经到家了，本来应该休息的时间居然还要去工作。

en: Life like this every day is too boring.
zh: 哎。。每天这样的生活太无趣了。

en: But if I want to save a lot of money， I have to bear with it and think about how to fix the bug.
zh: 但是我想要存一笔钱，还是先忍一下把，先想想如何修复bug把

en: Go to work first，no time to play on the computer
zh: 先去上班吧，没时间玩电脑了！

en: I'm so tired， let's play games for a while
zh: 好累啊，先玩吧游戏把

en: Just play for a while and stop playing
zh: 就玩一会就不玩了

en: Society is getting more and more involved and getting tired
zh: 社会越来越内卷，越来越累

en: If can go back in time， just start again
zh: 如果能回到过去，重新开始就好了

en: Wait， what's going on
zh: 等等，怎么回事

en: Ah ah ah ah ah ah ah. . . .
zh: 啊啊啊啊啊啊。。。。

en: Did not eat breakfast
zh: 早饭也没吃

en: Forget it， just eat on the road
zh: 算了路上随便吃点吧

en: Damn it's going to work overtime again
zh: 可恶又要加班了

en: I didn’t expect many people around to work overtime
zh: 没想到周围怎么多人还来加班

en: Why are there so many errors?
zh: 怎么全是报错

en: Staying up all night and working overtime continuously， I feel my body can’t stand it anymore， so I’ll take a leave today
zh: 连续的熬夜加班，我感觉身体已经受不了了，今天就请个假把

en: Maybe I will be better at home
zh: 回家或许思路会好一点

en: I can’t go back now， I’m going to ask the boss for a leave
zh: 现在还不能回去，我要先去找老板请个假

en: When can i get off work
zh: 什么时候才能下班啊

en: i have yellow poached eggs tomorrow morning
zh: 明天早上就吃流黄荷包蛋吧

en: I’m very uncomfortable with my boss for a long time
zh: 我其实已经看老板不爽很久了

en: Had it not been for the wife and children at home， I would have resigned long ago
zh: 要不是家里还有老婆孩子要养，我早就辞职了

en: You finally came
zh: 你终于来了

en: How is the work progress
zh: 交代的事情如何

en: Boss， the project is still a bit bug， it will take some time
zh: 老板，项目还有点bug，还需要一点时间

en: Well， I'm giving you a chance， it must be online tomorrow
zh: 呢行，我在给你一次机会，明天必须上线

en: thank you boss
zh: 谢谢老板

en: Boss，I have another business
zh: 老板我还有个事情

en: whats the matter
zh: 什么事情

en: Boss，I have been working overtime seriously recently and have some physical problems. Can I take a break?
zh: 老板我最近加班严重，身体有点问题，能不能休息一段时间

en: Do you know how many young people today envy your current job?
zh: 你知道现在的年轻人有多少羡慕你现在的工作么？

en: You don't do it， some people do it
zh: 你不干有的是人干

en: But seeing how hard you are，I will let you go back today and go home and finish the rest of the work.
zh: 不过看你蛮辛苦的样子，今天就让你先回去把，回家吧剩下的工作做完吧

en: Didn’t you approve you to take a half-day holiday， did you regret it?
zh: 不是批准你放假半天么，你难道反悔了？

en: I feel dizzy. .
zh: 头好晕。。

en: where is this place
zh: 这里是什么地方

en: I seemed to be sucked into the screen before
zh: 我之前好像被吸入的屏幕里面

en: Is this the world of games?
zh: 难道这里是游戏的世界？

en: Let meexplore around for clues
zh: 先四处探索一下寻找线索把

en: Skip the opening
zh: 跳过开场
